description:
Stepok Recomposit is state-of-the art photo composite software to assist photographers of all types. It allows you to cut an object from its background while maintaining all detail and transparency. 

Cutting out an object, masking an object or extracting an object from the background can be difficult task for many users but, Recomposit makes it easy. Providing advanced, professional methods such as one click chromakey masking, stroke based masking and inside/outside edge masking or trimap matting, Recomposit makes quality photo composition a breeze. The software also includes a complete environment for photo composing with expert, easy to use editing functions and tools. Recomposit supports Photoshop as a plugin too.

Info:

 - Use serial to register
 - Please manually copy  8bf files to the Photoshop Plugin folder.
